              },
              "displayName": "Arun Suresh",
              "active": true,
              "timeZone": "America/Los_Angeles"
            },
            "body": "Sure, feel free to take over. Yup, we would need YARN-3409 to get to some level of completion. But we need to decide if we want to allow ALL attributes to be scope-able or just a pre-configured subset.",
            "updateAuthor": {
              "self": "https://issues.apache.org/jira/rest/api/2/user?username=asuresh",
              "name": "asuresh",
              "key": "asuresh",
              "avatarUrls": {
